          "settings": {
            "faq_title": "Why should I add package protection to my order?",
            "faq_des": "<p>At checkout, you'll have the option to add package protection to your order. This helps safeguard your products from loss or damage during transit. While we package every item with great care, unexpected shipping issues can happen. We encourage adding package protection to ensure your handcrafted products arrive safely. Your satisfaction matters to us, and we want you to love every purchase.</p>"
          }
        },
        "faq_LitriH": {
          "type": "faq",
          "settings": {
            "faq_title": "My package is missing. Now what?",
            "faq_des": "<p>We're sorry that happened. If your package never arrived or is missing, please contact us at <a href=\"mailto:support@fleuriation.com\">support@fleuriation.com</a>, and we'll gladly help guide you toward the best solution. We also recommend adding package protection at checkout for additional peace of mind.</p>"
          }
        },
        "faq_nMQWmf": {
          "type": "faq",
          "settings": {
            "faq_title": "What is Fleuriation's return policy?",
            "faq_des": "<p>At Fleuriation, we offer a 30-day return policy. You have 30 days from the date you receive your order to request a return.</p>"
          }
        },
        "faq_Bm7kQd": {
          "type": "faq",
          "settings": {
            "faq_title": "What is your return and exchange process?",
            "faq_des": "<p>1. We accept returns on eligible items within 30 days of delivery.</p><p>2. Items must be <strong><em>unused, unopened, and in their original packaging.</em></strong></p><p>3. A valid proof of purchase (such as your order number) is required to process your return.</p>"
          }
        },
        "faq_Ds4LpW": {
          "type": "faq",
          "settings": {
            "faq_title": "What items are considered non-returnable?",
            "faq_des": "<p>1. Due to the nature of our products, opened skincare products, herbal blends, and custom-made items cannot be returned or exchanged.</p><p>2. Gift cards and promotional items are non-returnable.</p>"
          }
        },
        "faq_Hx8VrN": {
          "type": "faq",
          "settings": {
            "faq_title": "How do I initiate a return?",
            "faq_des": "<p>1. Email our customer care team at <a href=\"mailto:support@fleuriation.com\">support@fleuriation.com</a> with your order number and reason for your return.</p><p>2. Once your request is approved, we'll provide return instructions.</p><p>3. Customers are responsible for return shipping costs unless the return is due to our error, such as an incorrect or damaged product.</p>"
          }
        },
        "faq_Qz5MtE": {
          "type": "faq",
          "settings": {
            "faq_title": "How long is the refund process?",
            "faq_des": "<p>1. Once we receive and inspect your returned item, we'll notify you whether your refund has been approved.</p><p>2. Approved refunds will be issued to your original payment method within 5–7 business days.</p><p>If you have any questions, please contact us at <a href=\"mailto:support@fleuriation.com\">support@fleuriation.com</a>.</p>"
